      <title>伯克希尔减持近一半股份后，苹果供应商股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/apple-supplier-stocks-slump-after-berkshire-nearly-halves-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伯克希尔哈撒韦公司 (Berkshire Hathaway Inc.) 几乎减持了苹果公司一半的股份，导致苹果公司供应商的股价暴跌。周一，苹果公司股价下跌，而与此同时，市场普遍出现抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-05/apple-supplier-stocks-slump-after-berkshire-nearly-halves-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 06:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
