    <item>
      <title>油价从七个月低点回落，因股市暴跌抵消了伊朗风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于中东地区紧张局势加剧，金融市场普遍出现抛售，交易员担心伊朗可能对以色列采取报复性打击，油价从七个月来的最低收盘价延续跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-5</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 23:10:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Novo 的供应紧缩、德国的痛苦：欧洲、中东和非洲地区收益周展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/novo-s-supply-crunch-germany-s-pain-emea-earnings-week-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲最有价值的公司诺和诺德公司 (Novo Nordisk A/S) 可能在本周发布财报时跟随其他制药商上调业绩指引，因为该公司正竞相满足市场对其减肥药物 Wegovy 的巨大需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/novo-s-supply-crunch-germany-s-pain-emea-earnings-week-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 07:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
